These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, prince, bongani
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, begonia, zinnia
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, satire, spy
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, writing, collecting
There are 3 different nationalities: german, pakistani, polish
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, train, trike
 1. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the person who growsazalea##5
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 3. the bongani-smoker is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
 4. the person watching crime movies is the polish##1
 5. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
 6. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the german##3
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 8. the person driving the train is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the bongani-smoker##5
10. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
11. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who growsbegonia##8
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the fonseca-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Cigar          | fonseca | prince | bongani    |
| Flower           | azalea | begonia   | zinnia     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | satire   | spy       |
| Hobby   | writing    | collecting   | singing     |
| Nationality   | polish    | german   | pakistani |
| Transport     | trike     | airplane | train     |

