.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, photography
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, lavender, blue
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, metal, trance
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, bus, boat
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, poker
 1. the fan of house is not to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
 2. the person driving the bus is the person playing domino##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of metal##1
 4. the person who likes blue is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
 5. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
 6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 8. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the bus is not the fan of house##6
10. the fan of metal is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
11. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
12. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
13. the person playing domino is somewhere between the person who likes lavender and the owner of the goldfish##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | photography | filmmaking | card-games |
| Color           | lavender     | amber     | blue     |
| Music-Genre   | house       | metal      | trance     |
