 8. the person who likes white is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person who's hobby is chess##7
 9. the person who likes purple is not the person drinking mirinda##6
10. the person driving the snowmobile is between the mexican and the person driving the tram##2
11. the chinese is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |     3     |
| Beverage      | 7up       | mirinda         | cola      |
| Hobby         | chess     | drawing         | baking    |
| Color           | purple  | white | amber |
| Nationality   | mexican    | chinese        | polish      |
| City         | miami  | london        | berlin    |
| Transport     | quad-bike | snowmobile      | tram      |

