 5. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##8
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is the owner of the mouse##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
10. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
11. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
13. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in february##1
